                    "text": "The \"Pandit Dindayal Upadhyay Awas Yojana (Developing Caste Welfare) (NT-DNT)\" is a welfare scheme by the Social Justice and Empowerment Department of Gujarat. Under this scheme, eligible applicants from the Nomadic Tribe (NT) and Denotified Tribe (DNT) are given up to ₹1,20,000/- for constructing a house. Priority is given to individuals from BPL families."
